-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Troubleshooting Common Issues
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Check if forwarding is enabled
cat /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward
cat /proc/sys/net/ipv6/conf/all/forwarding

2. Check nftables rules
sudo nft list ruleset







